      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POWER AFFECT (4) boasts strong form at this course and distance having won three times from six starts. Below best last time at Shepparton (22.96) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5, finishing a 6 length fifth. Looks suited and should go close. BRAGGING RIGHTS (6) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when third (22.28) at Ballarat in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. PAW ENNA (2) showed good pace from out wide and was prominent early but began to paddle and faded out of it when 8th at Sale in Grade 5 company. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. INGA AMY (8) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
